    "Numbers above the bars indicate the number of differentially expressed genes in that specific intersection.",
    "B Pairwise Spearman correlations of log 2 fold changes for all genes investigated in this study, for P. palmivora treatment versus control (top) and between resistant versus susceptible genotypes (bottom).",
    "The bottom off-diagonal is the Spearman correlation coefficient.",
    "The top off-diagonal is the correlation coefficient depicted as an ellipse, the shape of which depends on the size of the coefficient.",
    "Asterisks indicate statistical significance (p < 0.001), tested using Spearman's rho."
